tokenizer,Tokenizer,Convert text, messages, or arrays of messages into arrays of token numbers using cl200k_base or cl100k_base tokenizers.
tool,Tool,Define a tool / function call for a LLM to use.
tool-cleanup,Tool Cleanup,Ensures all tool calls in a conversation have corresponding tool responses. Inserts synthetic responses for any unanswered tool calls before user messages or at the end of the conversation.
truncate-by-tokens,Truncate by Tokens,Keep only the most recent messages that fit within the specified token limit.
truncate-by-tokens-from-start,Truncate by Tokens from Start,Keep only the first messages that fit within the specified token limit.
